Package: simswjm
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Data from Stepped Wedge Longitudinal Trials
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Alessandro", 
         family = "Gasparini", 
         email = "alessandro.gasparini@reddooranalytics.se", 
         role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Red Door Analytics AB", role = c("cph"))
  )
Description: Simulate data from stepped wedge cluster randomised trials with
  continuous, binary, or counts outcomes. Scenarios with non-informative and
  informative dropout can be accommodated.
